DATA CENTRE唔運作, 係咪等於個市就要停?<br />\n<br />\n一半一半<br />\n第一半, HKEX SERVER會有另一個BACKUP CENTRE, 起個SERVER<br />\n但另一半, 有部分嘅劵行好似上面咁講, 放咗SERVER去將軍澳個DATA CENTRE, 佢自己唔會再有另一個BACKUP SERVER<br />\n<br />\n唔計大行, 將會有好多劵行嘅客無得做TRADE<br />\n唔係散客呀, 係講緊用好多錢去買SERVICE 做ALGO TRADING嘅大客呀"},{"pid":"95888716e30b9fc466614306f10cbf15f49c2c68","tid":1710562,"uid":120431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cadc06ab5cfd7f1e4a1e465f39b243b7a4522c9","tid":1710562,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70c58e0170773692f59e06f28b136071dbf4db77","tid":1710562,"uid":216683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:44:35.000Z","msg":"無<br />\n<br />\n佢自己有HOST個DATA CENTRE, 係將軍澳<br />\n好多劵行都會買HKEX個SERVICE,<br />\n將D做ALGO TRADING, 股票期指期權SERVER放入去DATA CENTRE<br />\n<br />\n所以中環佔領咗都無用<br />\n第一, 其他行都可以用CLIENT 連去DATA CENTRE 個SERVER做SETTING, 繼續做TRADE<br />\n第二, HKEX D SERVER都唔係中環<br />\n<br />\n咁將軍澳個DATA CENTRE唔運作, 係咪等於個市就要停?<br />\n<br />\n一半一半<br />\n第一半, HKEX SERVER會有另一個BACKUP CENTRE, 起個SERVER<br />\n但另一半, 有部分嘅劵行好似上面咁講, 放咗SERVER去將軍澳個DATA CENTRE, 佢自己唔會再有另一個BACKUP SERVER<br />\n<br />\n唔計大行, 將會有好多劵行嘅客無得做TRADE<br />\n唔係散客呀, 係講緊用好多錢去買SERVICE 做ALGO TRADING嘅大客呀"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:48:28.000Z","msg":"俾多少少INFORMATION<br />\n<br />\nTKO DATA CENTRE<br />\n<br />\nHKEX SERVER &lt;-(內聯)-&gt; 劵行SERVER &lt;-(網絡)-&gt; 中環/其他區CLIENT<br />\n<br />\n如果將軍澳 HKEX DATA centre down..咁HKEX SERVER同劵行SERVER就行唔到<br />\n<br />\n當HKEX 起BACKUP SERVER: HKEX SERVER(BACKUP) ????? <br />\n因為劵行無MAIN任何SERVER, 所以唔會起得到, 駁去BACKUP HKEX SERVER"},{"pid":"1ba8f2198be915ba78200424c8437fa2c0f01497","tid":1710562,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cadc06ab5cfd7f1e4a1e465f39b243b7a4522c9","tid":1710562,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70c58e0170773692f59e06f28b136071dbf4db77","tid":1710562,"uid":216683,"